reviews.text: Today I ate a Pork knuckle udon at this restaurant. The waiter delivered was a very hot hot pot. Even after I waited for a while, the soup and noodles were still very hot. Frankly, I don't like to eat too hot food because it is harmful to health. According to experts, eating too hot food can burn the tongue, esophagus and throat, and even cause cancer.

This is a nice mixture of Japanese / HK style restaurant.
The menu is full of choices ranging from rice, noodles, Sushi, soup etc.
This restaurant is busy at lunch time so you may have to wait a little
Other than that, the food is good quality for the price, you can eat here for $50 to $70 HKD
The udon is fine. Not much surprise.

result.name: 甘味讚岐手打烏冬

reviews.text:
突然日本癮發作，近近地係香港仔揾左間甘味日式餐廳。哩到日式美食多樣化，刺身、壽司、烏冬同多款曰式小食都有。

先點左款日式沙律做前菜。哩個沙律份量好多，菜好新鮮加埋沙律醬非常開胃。墨魚餅比想像中大份，肉質好淋，唔算彈牙，不過好有墨魚肉香味👍🏻。

曰式雞軟骨餃子，餃子皮薄，外皮煎到好香脆。雞軟骨饀料脆卜卜，比起豬肉饀料更加有口感。

鐘意食鯖魚因為骨少，啖啖魚肉。煎香左既鯖魚上面加左少少鹽同檸檬汁會減少左魚腥味，味道更好。

滑蛋蟹籽巨型蟹柳手打烏冬，整個湯底味道甜甜地。蛋同巨型蟹柳夾左一起，份量超多，好食。

哩個飯用鐵盤裝起，可以保持飯既温度。牛肉味道超級入味又淋。值得一讚。
香港仔這間分店味道做得不太好，感觉不到厨师用心做每道食品，餃子炸得黑，鳥東煮得糊了，地方還算乾凈，服务态度也不是很好，服务員對客人爱理不理的态度。
手打烏冬唔覺有乜特別…壽司就真係特別，體積好迷你，但價錢貴過食元氣…叫做食過囉，無下次了…

Today I ate a Pork knuckle udon at this restaurant. The waiter delivered was a very hot hot pot. Even after I waited for a while, the soup and noodles were still very hot. Frankly, I don't like to eat too hot food because it is harmful to health. According to experts, eating too hot food can burn the tongue, esophagus and throat, and even cause cancer.

This is a nice mixture of Japanese / HK style restaurant.
The menu is full of choices ranging from rice, noodles, Sushi, soup etc.
This restaurant is busy at lunch time so you may have to wait a little
Other than that, the food is good quality for the price, you can eat here for $50 to $70 HKD
